title: Disgusting bug with rune page
body:
20 minutes waiting in queue to dodge lobby and wait another 20 minutes. Cuz of this. 
Riooot. 
Its like third time I've got this in last time.
http://oi66.tinypic.com/25qc4r5.jpg

replies.body: It's a bit of a bug they've been looking into, but I would definitely be sure to submit a bug report first off! It'd be worth it to post this screenshot over in Report a Bug as well, but go ahead and do me a favor by trying a quick client repair followed by checking your rune pages for anything named similarly or with special characters.
